{"tid":1201286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞] 建制議員全身而退有賴秘密通道","createTime":"2019-06-11T03:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:24:08.000Z","uid":57355,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3198b8f6ef7ef5af89bae083d62a46e241df24","tid":1201286,"uid":57355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:50:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=84405&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D84405%26refer%3D&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDx4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=b95d5476\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D84405%26refer%3D&h=78fe3a42\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=84405&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"d919307e8e1a400c69c40292d39337d8fd9114a1","tid":1201286,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc16e0bdc82f54ca38c4d03959f6a1169a14f4d7","tid":1201286,"uid":146813,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:01:08.000Z","msg":"周三立法會討論是否引用特權法迫政府交出行會文件，晚上有萬人集會包圍立法會，這一夜，揭露了啟用近兩年的立法會大樓的秘密通道。<br />\n<br />\n政情會帶大家看一下，一班建制派議員，是如何從立法會大樓內，越過重圍，瞬間消失。關鍵就是在立法會停車場內的秘道，停車場有兩個出口，我們分別帶大家看看。<br />\n<br />\n這個是議員日常出入的出口，駛上去就是政府總部的公民廣場，周三晚群眾集會的地方。<br />\n<br />\n這個閘後面就是秘道，要開放就要通知立法會秘書處，以及政府總部的人。<br />\n<br />\n而大閘後面，就是政府總部西面，周三晚，立法會散會後，立法會就開放這條通道，讓議員可以無阻地駕駛自己的座駕離開大樓。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，很多議員都是當晚才知道有這條通道，大家都讚歎是偉大發明，有些人還說枉他們擔心好像高鐵時一樣被圍困。我們問過秘書長陳維安，他表示這條秘道會在緊急時開放，強調主要是讓議員使用，未有官員用過。"},{"pid":"599bc892e60333cc19ce436e42215ee893064312","tid":1201286,"uid":85774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"屌佢班建制垃圾 揸波子！！！！！！"},{"pid":"890c8cd580e3a52bb4bcba9ad11dbf49f709ab8f","tid":1201286,"uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"走到和尚走唔到廟，希望佢地家人平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3758e36429c49bcb2cba1644893ab6b39ffc528","tid":1201286,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"890c8cd580e3a52bb4bcba9ad11dbf49f709ab8f","tid":1201286,"uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"走到和尚走唔到廟，希望佢地家人平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:06:27.000Z","msg":"始終都要返屋企啩"},{"pid":"74c8847a808bef346935e6b0a84c93c1f2219c44","tid":1201286,"uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e3758e36429c49bcb2cba1644893ab6b39ffc528","tid":1201286,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"890c8cd580e3a52bb4bcba9ad11dbf49f709ab8f","tid":1201286,"uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"走到和尚走唔到廟，希望佢地家人平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:06:27.000Z","msg":"始終都要返屋企啩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"家人平安嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e8dd4243233c515172aff17504a0f972b7ca0e","tid":1201286,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"890c8cd580e3a52bb4bcba9ad11dbf49f709ab8f","tid":1201286,"uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"走到和尚走唔到廟，希望佢地家人平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/